    <p class="commit-title ">
        <a href="/msurguy/ladda-bootstrap/commit/02e23a8f38714f80edfbcedb4302789d9b538032" class="message" data-pjax="true" title="Cleanup and update Ladda to 0.9.4

Remove bower and npm configs since this is just an example of using ladda with Bootstrap and no new functionality is given.">Cleanup and update Ladda to 0.9.4</a>
        <span class="hidden-text-expander inline"><a href="#" class="js-details-target">…</a></span>
    </p>
      <div class="commit-desc"><pre>Remove bower and npm configs since this is just an example of using ladda with Bootstrap and no new functionality is given.</pre></div>
